OL,4,G2300FTaggart
OL,5,     GWhen Jimmy Catto, one time
OL,6,     Ghitman, is released after a
OL,7,     Gtwenty year stretch, a series of
OL,8,     Gshootings begin to look like his
OL,9,     Ghandy work. Does Taggart know
OL,10,     Gbetter?
OL,11,G0145FJames May's Great Explorers
OL,12,     GJames rewrites stories of the
OL,13,     Ggreatest explorers in his
OL,14,     Ginimitable entertaining way,
OL,15,     Gstarting with Columbus - and how
OL,16,     Ghe merely 'stumbled across' two
OL,17,     Gcontinents, then took the spoils.
